text: Ann Henderson (1921–1976) was a Scottish sculptor. Ann Henderson may also refer to: *Ann Henderson (politician) (1941–2002), Australian politician *Ann Henderson (campaigner), Scottish campaigner and Rector-elect of the University of Edinburgh *Anne Henderson (born 1949), Australian writer *Anne Henderson (Northern Ireland), chair of the Parades Commission of Northern Ireland *Annie Henderson, I Know Why the Caged Bird Sings character ==See also== *Ann Henderson-Sellers (born 1952), professor at the Department of Environment and Geography at Macquarie University, Sydney
title: Ann Henderson (disambiguation)
